OL,3,CMan suffers life-threatening burn
OL,4,Cinjuries following suspected arson
OL,6,FA man has suffered "serious burn
OL,7,Finjuries" following suspected arson at
OL,8,Fa house in Swansea.
OL,10,FThe fire occurred on Gors Avenue,
OL,11,FTownhill, shortly after 1am on
OL,12,FWednesday 27 August.
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police confirmed the fire
OL,15,Fis believed to have been "started
OL,16,Fdeliberately" on the property's shared
OL,17,Fbalcony.
OL,19,FA local man was later taken to
OL,20,Fhospital, where his condition is
OL,21,Fbelieved to be "life-threatening".
